Module scenebuilder.core
Package com.oracle.javafx.scenebuilder.core.ui

Class AbstractFxmlController

java.lang.Object
com.oracle.javafx.scenebuilder.core.ui.AbstractPanelController
com.oracle.javafx.scenebuilder.core.ui.AbstractFxmlController
All Implemented Interfaces:
FxmlController
Direct Known Subclasses:
AbstractFxmlViewController, AbstractHierarchyPanelController, ContentPanelController, InfoPanelController, MessageBarController, MessagePanelController, SelectionBarController
public abstract class AbstractFxmlController
extends AbstractPanelController
implements FxmlController
AbstractFxmlController is the abstract base class for all the panel controller which build their UI components from an FXML file. Subclasses should provide a controllerDidLoadFxml() method in charge of finishing the initialization of the UI components loaded from the FXML file.
